looking to create a campaign and start testing

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble adding credits to your account. Could you please provide more details about the issue you're facing? For example, are you encountering an error message or is the option to add credits not available?

Got it! Let's start by resolving the issue with adding credits to your account. Could you please provide more details about the problem you're facing when trying to add credits? Once we get that sorted, I can guide you on creating and testing your campaign.
it says only account admin can add credits

It looks like you might not have the necessary permissions to add credits to your account. Only the account admin can add credits. If you are not the admin, please contact the person who manages your account to add credits for you. If you are the admin and still facing issues, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
can i speak with someone here?
I'm here to assist you with any questions or issues you have. Please let me know what specific help you need, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
do we get an account manager?

Yes, for businesses looking for more flexibility, we do offer post-pay solutions after 30 days of ad spend. You can reach out to an Account Manager to help get that set up. If you need assistance with this, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com.
